  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is the investigation of acute cardiovascular responses of marathon&#xD;
      runners after the completion of a marathon race (42.2 km), as well as of the determinants of&#xD;
      these changes.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
